# arvit-robot-control environment.
#
# The pure-logic core (extrinsics, timesync) and its tests need NO secrets and
# NO cloud keys. This file exists for container parity (project convention):
#
#   cp .env.example .env
#
# .env is gitignored; commit only .env.example. Secrets are passed ONLY via
# --env-file/.env, never baked into the image.

# ---- ROS 2 / DDS (deploy-target only; unused by the local test run) ----
# Set on the Orin so rclpy/CycloneDDS reach the robot's DDS domain.
# ROS_DOMAIN_ID=0
# RMW_IMPLEMENTATION=rmw_cyclonedds_cpp

# Optional: tweak pytest output inside the container.
# PYTEST_ADDOPTS=-q
